description:
At the beginning of December I want to say a big thank you to all of you. the last few month of the year was full of many new experiences for me, things that were completely unthinkable for me and beyond my control. I love you all
.
This is a artwork that I made at the end of December to respond to the year's transition from 2020 to 2021. Artwork "sujud" is my choice for 2021: Sadness, adversity to joy that revolves around things beyond my control. Then for a moment again dropped his forehead, towards the sky. “Death, leaving and leaving is not the end of everything, the end is the beginning of returning; build hope the hope that died to revive. Some of us walk and struggle hard enough to make a live to living. Run, walk and slow down, keep it up. Keep the silent fire in life even if it's dim at least it's keeping. And tell yourself that this time you fought and lived."
